data.description:
Welcome to your Dream Home! This stunning two-story residence, built in 2016, offers spacious living & exquisite features in every corner. Located in the prestigious Silverwood community of sunny South Florida, this property boasts a perfect blend of comfort, luxury, and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by over 2800 square feet of meticulously designed living space. The expansive floor plan includes 5 bedrooms & 3 bathrooms, providing ample room for the whole family. Entertain guests in style in the formal dining room w/ plenty of space for gatherings. The kitchen is a chef's delight, adorned w/ quartz counters, 42'' cabinets & stainless steel appliances. Tile flooring throughout the main areas adds a touch of sophistication while ensuring easy maintenance. One of the highlights of this home is its breathtaking waterfront views, creating a serene backdrop for everyday living. Imagine enjoying your morning coffee or hosting al fresco dinners on the covered patio and summer kitchen, overlooking the water.

The Silverwood community offers resort-style amenities, including a sparkling community pool & lush green spaces for recreation. With top-rated schools nearby and community parks within walking distance, this is truly a family-oriented neighborhood.

Constructed with CBS (Concrete Block and Stucco) for durability and peace of mind, this home also features in-law quarters, providing flexibility for multi-generational living arrangements.

Conveniently located, this property offers easy access to shopping centers, schools, places of worship, and major airports, making it an ideal choice for modern living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home!
